title: Fort Dupont Park: Photo Gallery
body: Photo Gallery                    Community Garden   21 Photos  Fort Dupont Park's Community Garden was established in 1974. Today the National Park Service manages over 100 garden plots, two bee hives and a demonstration garden. Rangers lead tours, interpretive programs and volunteer events throughout the year.          Summer Theatre Concert Series   13 Photos  40th Anniversary of Fort Dupont Park's Summer Theatre Concert Series
